      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "KIOWA ICON (6) missed the frame and safely held latest finishing 8th at this track following on from a win (22.29) there the start prior. Solid record here at the distance winning two races. Has claims if she runs up to expectations. ALFREDO (7) turned in a moderate performance last time when sixth at Ballarat over 390m behind Paw Ortiz (22.45) in a Grade 5. Was in the money the start prior. Solid formlines coming through his last run. A forward showing wouldn't surprise. DEVINGTON (8) finished in the minors last time but only a few starts back pushed the clock when winning over 450m at Ballarat, taking a Grade 5 H in a handy 25.29. Expected to feature on best figures. WHIZZ MAXIMUS (4) pinged the lids and wasn't headed last time. Right in the mix again.",
